just put up all the resists and regen you have.. that helps against casters. casters are : stonechanter - cleric, dirttracker - mage, flamedrowser - wizard, boneseer - necro, stalagknight - SK, and one more.. a shaman. stalagknights HT for either 321 or 331, depending on level.. be cautios.<br>
good luck :) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unazgrim.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nazgrim</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/8/01 12:20:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: No.  Gonna be very tough.</span><hr size=1> I think we should be ok now.  We'll have a lvl 40 druid,me(lvl 42), lvl 51 druid and a lvl 44 ranger.<br>
